– Brand New Books Added:  Lady Ninja, A Love to Hide and College Desires 2 are waiting for you. Enjoy fresh new stories with new characters. Control their decisions and read the outcome of your choices!
– Unlockable Stories:  Done with one book? Start a new one!
– Greater Custom Experience: If you experience any problem while playing, let us know and we'll work on it!
